steps.name: I go to "https://google.com"
I click on the "search" element
I type "cucumberjs" in the "search" element
I press ENTER
the url should contain "https://www.google.com/search?"
I should see the "first result" element containing the text "cucumber/cucumber-js: Cucumber for JavaScript - GitHub"
